| Complainant | [Name or Anonymous] |
| Date of Report | [Date] |
| Method | [Verbal, written, hotline] |
| Alleged Respondent | [Name(s)] |
| Allegation Summary | [Brief description] |

### Initial Assessment
- [ ] Is this a complaint requiring investigation?
- [ ] What type of allegation (harassment, discrimination, policy, safety)?
- [ ] Does this require immediate action (safety, suspension)?
- [ ] Are there mandatory reporting requirements (safety, legal)?
- [ ] Potential witnesses identified?
- [ ] Documents to preserve?

### Immediate Actions Needed
- [ ] Ensure complainant safety
- [ ] Consider interim measures (separation, leave)
- [ ] Preserve relevant evidence
- [ ] Notify legal/HR leadership
- [ ] Issue litigation hold if needed

---

